== Main components ==
kworship is divided into a number of key components.

=== kworship ===
Main kworship application.

=== kworshipserver ===
The part that runs on the display and is controlled by the application.

=== kworshipdisplay ===
Display code.
This is essencially anything common between kworship and kworshipserver.

=== unipresent ===
Abstraction of control for different presentation software.
Used by kworship and kworshipserver.
Backends include:
* MS Powerpoint
* OO.org Impress
* kpresenter
* kworship's display

